            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[# SuperScreenshot 0.9.87

- 点击箭头、矩形或圆形后进入编辑状态。
- 箭头支持拖动首尾控制点调整方向和长度。
- 矩形和圆形支持通过四边、四角控制点调整大小。
- 保留拖动主体移动标注和点击空白取消选中。

---

- Added editable selection states for arrows, rectangles, and ellipses.
- Resize arrows using start and end handles.
- Resize shapes using edge and corner handles.
- Preserved body dragging and deselection by clicking empty space.
]]></description>
